            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Phuket Crocodile Farm and Crocodile Show"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "The first and largest crocodile farm in Phuket is not just a show, it is a huge center dedicated to these amazing animals.First, you will be guided through the Crocodile Museum. This is the only museum dedicated to these reptiles. Then a delightful crocodile show will leave an impression for a long time. And of course, here you can visit the souvenir center of crocodile leather products. Crocodile leather products have been considered an attribute of rich and stylish people for centuries. All products are made from animals raised or caught under a special license in the Kingdom of Thailand.Everyone knows that crocodile leather is used in the manufacture of clothing, shoes and bags. But few people know that crocodile meat is quite pleasant to the taste and is a cross between pork and chicken.In addition to crocodile leather products, the store offers products made from the skin of other exotic animals: snakes, stingrays, elephants or monitor lizards."
          }
        ]
      },
